@startuml
actor Staff
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "staff-service" as StaffService
database "MySQL Staff DB" as StaffDB

Staff -> Gateway: POST /api/staff/login/
Gateway -> StaffService: POST /staff/login/
StaffService -> StaffDB: Verify username/password
StaffDB --> StaffService: Staff account
StaffService --> Gateway: JWT access/refresh
Gateway --> Staff: Login response
@enduml
